      • SpaceTaker

        public SpaceTaker()
        Default constructor. Set the worker thread as a Daemon thread

      • SpaceTaker

        public SpaceTaker(SpaceTaker.SpaceTakerData data,
          ExecutorService pool)
        This is a Constructor. It executes the default constructor plus set the provider worker data and executor service pool. The transaction lease time is set and space time out time is established.
        Parameters:
        data - SpaceDispatcher data
        pool - Executor service provides methods to manage termination and tracking progress of one or more asynchronous tasks
